name: AGOQ 21.1
description:
5 rounds for time:

• 15 handstand push-ups
• 15 dumbbell shoulder-to-overheads
• 15-cal. row

50-lb. dumbbells

Time cap: 20 min.

*Occupational Games athletes must complete the 16-54 variation of the workout.

For full details on each age group category and movement standards, visit https://games.crossfit.com/workouts/onlinequalifiers/2021
